    dc:description "Figure 9. Kartvelobia sinuata sp. nov., Imereti, Satsiskvilo, Turchusmtha, morphology of the reproductive organs A-D morphology of the penis E female renal and pallial section of reproductive organs. Bc - bursa copulatrix; cbc - duct of bursa copulatrix; ga - albuminoid gland; gn - nidamental gland; gp - gonoporus; ov - oviduct; ovl - loop of oviduct; rs - receptaculum seminis; vc - ventral channel. Photograph and drawing A. Falniowski." ;
